Praise be to God, please come in.

515
00:29:57,000 --> 00:29:58,000
يلا.
 
Let's go.

516
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:59,000
أهلا وسهلا.
 
Welcome.

517
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:00,000
يا رب.
 
Oh Lord.

518
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:05,000
